{
  "stem": "1895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I could think of is at the age of 12, why could I not be a part of such tremendous might?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I couldn't reconcile the fact that this might is coming into-- against me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's coming in against us, because we knew that the Germans had no good intentions toward Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But these were the emotional feelings of a young boy, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which could be overcome soon by other things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Immediately, we felt the strain and we got restricted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we could not operate the same way as we did before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father couldn't go to work anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He lost his job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He lost his income.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember my oldest brother Abram was able to go to the bank I think a day or two after they entered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was able to withdraw 500 zloties, which he had on his bank account.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for some reason he beat the clock, because I remember like a day or two later the announcement came out that Jews cannot withdraw money from banks.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he managed to withdraw the 500 zloties.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I also remember that my father in his wisdom had brought home from the warehouse that he worked out of several packages of leather, soft leather, which his firm made.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he just brought it home for the first time that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And those several packages of leather became an underpinning for our-- for our survival, because money-- inflation ran up immediately high.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if you had money it became worthless pretty soon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, it took maybe a couple months that money became almost worthless.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- so anything that you had to barter, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that was valuable.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
